Entries.default: "I've got sea legs and land legs, but whatever this is? No good. I'll try not to vomit on you this time, Ishi."
"Ekera, I say the animancer's tower has seen better days."
"Tell me this is the last time we trust these animancers."
"Belfetto! It worked! Well, perhaps it only half-worked, but... oh, this is not where we are intended to be, either."
"I be half sure this ain't Neketaka. But only half."
"I'm about to be sick... And this sure doesn't look like an animancer's tower to me."
"Hm. True physical translation. I suppose I owe Flaune that drink."
